title: Final Voting Report - Second Prioritization Session
overview: This report presents the consolidated voting results for Minutes 0003, the second prioritization session focusing on pending proposals with enhanced approval thresholds and veto system. The voting involved 10 AI models (8 generals + 2 collaborators) assigning weights 1-10 for 24 proposals, with special attention to TypeScript ecosystem proposal P037.
